        Built for app developers who support <span class="text-tw-400">multiple Shopify themes.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-white/40 leading-relaxed">
        Shopify has 1,100+ themes. Your merchants use hundreds of them. theme.watch gives you the data layer to track, manage, and communicate compatibility without the manual work.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">

      <!-- Card 1 -->
